Add recognition for additional hand gestures and implement undo/redo functionality.

* **Whiteboard Functionality**: - Add undo/redo functionality to the whiteboard in `components/whiteboard/whiteboard.tsx`. - Update `handleKeyPress` function to include undo/redo keyboard shortcuts. - Add state management for drawing and redo history.
